                     <interp inst="t18320216-242-person2016" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I live in Britannia-street. I was at my window - I went down; the prisoner was brought back, and I took charge of him - I found on him, one crown, one half-crown, some shillings and sixpences, and half pence; in all 14s., but no purse.</p>
